Syd Saylor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Syd_Saylor 0 Syd Saylor (born Leo Sailor; March 24, 1895 – December 21, 1962) was an American comedic actor and movie cowboy sidekick who appeared in 395 films and television series between 1926 and 1962.
